OL,3,C'You can do it': Princess of Wales
OL,4,Ccelebrates patient completing
OL,5,Cchemotherapy
OL,7,FThe Princess of Wales celebrated with
OL,8,Fa young mum as she marked completing
OL,9,Fher chemotherapy on a visit to a
OL,10,Fcancer ward.
OL,12,FKate joined patients, staff and family
OL,13,Fat The Christie NHS Foundation Trust
OL,14,Fin Manchester, where she congratulated
OL,15,FClaire Lorente, 30, who rang the bell
OL,16,Fto signify the end of her cancer
OL,17,Ftreatment.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
