PN,39902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1780683078
OL,3,C'You can do it': Princess of Wales
OL,4,Ccelebrates patient completing
OL,5,Cchemotherapy
OL,7,FThe princess visited the centre -
OL,8,Fwhich is the largest single site
OL,9,Fcancer centre in Europe and treats
OL,10,F60,000 patients a year - to see the
OL,11,Fwide range of holistic care available.
OL,13,FMs Lorente and her partner Pablo
OL,14,Freceived hugs from Kate along with her
OL,15,Fson, Enzo, as she congratulated Claire
OL,16,Fon completing treatment.
OL,18,FKate said to Ms Lorente: "Well done
OL,19,Fyou. What a journey. It's been a tough
OL,20,Fone, yeah?
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1780683078
OL,3,C'You can do it': Princess of Wales
OL,4,Ccelebrates patient completing
OL,5,Cchemotherapy
OL,7,F"You have done brilliantly. Well done."
OL,9,FShe also embraced Pablo and said:
OL,10,F"Well done. It's just as hard for the
OL,11,Ffamily and loved ones", before turning
OL,12,Fto Enzo to say: "Isn't mummy brave."
OL,14,FKate then joined the crowd to clap and
OL,15,Fencourage a tearful Ms Lorente to ring
OL,16,Fthe bell as she said: "You can do it."
OL,18,FThe princess revealed she was in
OL,19,Fremission after receiving chemotherapy
OL,20,Ftreatment for an undisclosed form of
OL,21,Fcancer in 2025.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
