OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1780683078
OL,3,C'You can do it': Princess of Wales
OL,4,Ccelebrates patient completing
OL,5,Cchemotherapy
OL,7,FAmong holistic therapies available at
OL,8,FThe Christie - all free of charge to
OL,9,Fpatients and carers - are drop-in art
OL,10,Fclasses, a wellbeing garden and a
OL,11,Fchaplaincy service.
OL,13,FKate joined in an art session with six
OL,14,Fpatients who regularly use creative
OL,15,Fexpression to aid their recovery.
OL,17,FResident artist Patricia Mountfield
OL,18,Ftold her: "It can be very isolating
OL,19,Ffor some people.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1780683078
OL,3,C'You can do it': Princess of Wales
OL,4,Ccelebrates patient completing
OL,5,Cchemotherapy
OL,7,F"We have patients who come in and
OL,8,Fforget about everything while they are
OL,9,Fin here."
OL,11,FKate said: "It changes you in so many
OL,12,Fways physically but also emotionally
OL,13,Fand psychologically, and actually
OL,14,Ffinding ways to express that and to
OL,15,Fexplore that is quite difficult.
OL,17,F"To do this in a clinical setting is
OL,18,Freally important."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
