PN,39906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1780683078
OL,3,C'You can do it': Princess of Wales
OL,4,Ccelebrates patient completing
OL,5,Cchemotherapy
OL,7,FAfter visiting the centre's wellbeing
OL,8,Fgarden, Kate completed her visit at
OL,9,FThe Christie's Teenage and Young Adult
OL,10,F(TYA) unit, where young patients can
OL,11,Ftake part in social and recreational
OL,12,Factivities with facilities including a
OL,13,Fmusic room, gym and lounge.
OL,15,FOutside the centre, one young
OL,16,Fpatient's mother told Kate her son had
OL,17,Fbeen following the princess' journey
OL,18,Fthrough cancer treatment to inspire
OL,19,Fhim.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1780683078
OL,3,C'You can do it': Princess of Wales
OL,4,Ccelebrates patient completing
OL,5,Cchemotherapy
OL,7,FShe said: "He said one day he will be
OL,8,Fable to ring the bell just like you."
OL,10,FRoger Spencer, Chief Executive of The
OL,11,FChristie NHS Foundation Trust, said:
OL,12,F"We were delighted to welcome Her
OL,13,FRoyal Highness The Princess of Wales.
OL,15,F"Having cancer affects every area of
OL,16,Fsomeone's life, and we're proud to
OL,17,Fhave a person-centred approach to care
OL,18,Fthat focuses on the individual, and
OL,19,Fnot just their diagnosis.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1780683078
OL,3,C'You can do it': Princess of Wales
OL,4,Ccelebrates patient completing
OL,5,Cchemotherapy
OL,7,F"Our art room, complementary therapy
OL,8,Fservice and TYA unit mean so much to
OL,9,Fpeople here, and it was an honour to
OL,10,Fintroduce the princess to the patients
OL,11,Fand staff involved."
OL,13,FFollowing the visit, Kate posted on
OL,14,Fsocial media: "Thank you to everyone
OL,15,Fat The Christie for such a moving
OL,16,Fvisit today.
OL,18,F"Meeting patients, families and staff
OL,19,Fwas a powerful reminder that healing
OL,20,Fis about so much more than treatment
OL,21,Falone.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1780683078
OL,3,C'You can do it': Princess of Wales
OL,4,Ccelebrates patient completing
OL,5,Cchemotherapy
OL,7,F"A cancer diagnosis affects every part
OL,8,Fof life, in mind, body and the deeper
OL,9,Fpart of ourselves. The way we process
OL,10,Ffear, uncertainty and change is deeply
OL,11,Fpersonal.
OL,13,F"The Christie's commitment to holistic
OL,14,Fcare, from art therapy and wellbeing
OL,15,Fspaces to emotional and spiritual
OL,16,Fsupport, helps people navigate not
OL,17,Fonly illness, but the profound impact
OL,18,Fit can have on quality of life.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1780683078
OL,3,C'You can do it': Princess of Wales
OL,4,Ccelebrates patient completing
OL,5,Cchemotherapy
OL,7,F"These services empower patients to
OL,8,Fplay an active role in their recovery
OL,9,Fand wellbeing, reminding us that care
OL,10,Fshould always be centred on the whole
OL,11,Fperson.
OL,13,F"Thank you for sharing your stories
OL,14,Fwith me, and for the compassion,
OL,15,Fcreativity and dedication shown every
OL,16,Fday across the hospital. C."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
